  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户旅程的时序图，核心流程是：用户在前端选择角色和阶段，然后前端调用API，API再去调度GPT-5.1，最后把渲染结果返回给用户。关键是中间有个叫Zyno的编排层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Frontend",
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (GPT-5.1)",
        "Choose persona/phase",
        "Orchestrate",
        "Render interactions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，四个参与者：User、Frontend、API v1、还有Zyno。我想确认一下，Zyno和API v1是分开的两个participant吗？看您的描述，API收到请求后去调用Zyno做编排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (GPT-5.1)",
        "Orchestrate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Zyno是GPT-5.1的实例，专门做prompt+schema的编排。API v1是独立的服务层，负责路由和聚合。所以调用链是：Frontend POST到API，API再去orchestrate Zyno。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Frontend",
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (GPT-5.1)",
        "POST /journeys/{id}/step",
        "Orchestrate (prompt + schema)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把四个participant按顺序排好了：User、Frontend、API v1、Zyno。第一条消息是User到Frontend的\"Choose persona/phase\"，然后是Frontend到API的POST请求。接下来画API到Zyno的orchestrate调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Frontend",
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (GPT-5.1)",
        "Choose persona/phase",
        "POST /journeys/{id}/step",
        "Orchestrate (prompt + schema)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "返回路径要注意：Zyno返回的是JourneyStepResponse，JSON格式，里面包含ui_blocks和next_state。API要把这两样东西传给Frontend，最后Frontend渲染给用户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zyno (GPT-5.1)",
        "API v1",
        "Frontend",
        "User",
        "JourneyStepResponse (JSON)",
        "ui_blocks + next_state",
        "Render interactions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到。Zyno到API是虚线返回JourneyStepResponse，API到Frontend也是虚线返回ui_blocks和next_state，最后Frontend到User是实线的Render interactions。这样区分同步调用和异步响应对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zyno (GPT-5.1)",
        "API v1",
        "Frontend",
        "User",
        "JourneyStepResponse (JSON)",
        "ui_blocks + next_state",
        "Render interactions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Zyno返回和API返回都用虚线箭头，表示响应。Frontend到User的渲染是实线，因为那是主动触发的交互更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zyno (GPT-5.1)",
        "API v1",
        "Frontend",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程：用户选角色→前端POST→API编排Zyno→GPT返回JSON→API提取ui_blocks和next_state给前端→前端渲染交互。所有箭头和标签都按您说的画好了。",
